    "attributes": {
        "action": "Set limits on the length of lane closures for roadworks",
        "additional_details": "We believe that continuous lane closure disruption may cause:\r\n- Increased potential for accidents\r\n- Reduced access for emergency vehicles\r\n- Delayed business deliveries\r\n- Difficulty planning journeys\r\n- Increased journey times\r\n- Personal stress\r\n- Road rage\r\n- Lateness for medical appointments, work, school, flights, etc.\r\n- Damage to the environment due to pollution from concentrated stationary traffic ",
        "background": "Set limits for roadworks on motorways and A roads including:\r\n- Limiting lane closures to 3 miles maximum on motorways, 1 mile on A roads. \r\n- No roadworks or lane closures allowed within 20 miles of other works.\r\n- All work areas resourced 24 hours a day in non-residential areas until completion.",
